definitions.definition: The insertion of the penis (or similar object) during sexual intercourse .
examples: Any penetration , however slight, is sufficient to complete the offense.

definitions.definition: The act of penetrating a given situation with the mind or faculties; perception , discernment .
The act of progressing or moving forward through or into something.
A number or fraction that represents how many cards/decks will be dealt before shuffling, in contrast to the total number of cards/decks in play.
The proportion of the target audience who buy or use the specified product or service.

main_definition: The act of penetrating something. [from 15th c.]
secondary_definitions: The insertion of the penis (or similar object) during sexual intercourse . [from 17th c.]
The act of penetrating a given situation with the mind or faculties; perception , discernment . [from 17th c.]
The act of progressing or moving forward through or into something.
